title: Group Therapy: He Wants Kids, She Wants to Wait
description: A listener has been dating her boyfriend for a couple years.  They're both 22 and he is saying he wants to have kids in their 20s.  She wants to be able to have fun in her 20s, travel, etc, but she really loves her boyfriend so she's wondering if she's being selfish saying that she wants to wait until her 30s.
